column5: Got this sent to me on E-Mail from my cousin in Edmonton.  In case its true, take heed   http://www.cra-arc.gc.ca/nwsrm/lrts/2008/l080818-eng.html http://www.cra-arc.gc.ca/nwsrm/lrts/2008/l080818b-eng.pdf
Boy, you fill that out and they have everything and more than they need to mess up your life....  Thanks for the warning...  Burt
Oh Shnikes..  I didn't do my taxes yet!!  What do I do?!  AAAHHHHHH    HD
You mean you guys have to pay income taxes up there. I was just about to move north. I guess I will have to take another look at Florida and just grin and bear the winters down there....
Dont forget about the Hurricanes Billy Bob ...

Hurricanes, yes I drank many a hurricane the last time I was house boating on the Kawarthas. GREAT rum drink which is my favorite liquor.  (i was only kidding about moving south)   Stay Warm Up There Guys and I hope to see a few of you next spring/summer on Stony Lake  Bob
